name: ZOSU Zoo Demo
summary:
Demo of "ZOSU Zoo"
This is a sample of ZOSU Zoo, demo contents:
- ZOSU Zoo Land with a fence to restrict where you can go (no fence in full)
- Mixed reality and hand tracking preview area with sea turtles, and some plants and animals
- ZOSU Ocean area lobby

The full game has 140+ animals and over 60 jungle plants in various mixed reality and hand tracking experiences with mixed reality visual boundaries and save state options in some areas, and 30 ocean areas with a water jetpack.

Major update in July...
